title: Software Engineer Applicant
resume_text: Experienced Software Engineer with 5 years in full stack development. Proficient in JavaScript, React, Node.js, and Python. Built scalable microservices and REST APIs. Familiar with Docker, Kubernetes, and AWS. Strong problem-solving skills and mentorship experience.
job_description: We are looking for a Senior Software Engineer to join our team. Must have experience with React, Node.js, and cloud platforms like AWS. Knowledge of containerization (Docker/K8s) is a plus. Responsibilities include building robust APIs and mentoring junior developers.

title: Data Scientist Applicant
resume_text: Data Scientist with a Master's degree in Computer Science. Skilled in Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, and TensorFlow. Experience with data visualization using Matplotlib and Tableau. Strong background in statistics and machine learning algorithms.
job_description: Seeking a Data Scientist to analyze large datasets and build predictive models. Proficiency in Python and ML libraries (Scikit-learn, TensorFlow) required. Experience with big data tools like Spark is desirable.

title: Project Manager Applicant
resume_text: PMP certified Project Manager with 7 years of experience leading agile teams. Expert in JIRA, Confluence, and Scrum methodologies. Proven track record of delivering projects on time and within budget. Excellent communication and stakeholder management skills.
job_description: Hiring a Technical Project Manager to oversee software development lifecycles. Must be familiar with Agile/Scrum. PMP certification preferred. Strong leadership and communication skills essential.
